data.description: Welcome to Windy Side Farm and The c1781 Josiah Clark Homestead!  This historic property is one you'll need to see in person to truly appreciate.  The main house has the charm of The 1700's with wide pine floors, multiple fire places and exposed posts and beams and has been updated to modern day standards.  With a total of 10 mini-splits, there is no lack of efficiency for heating and cooling.  The first floor offers the master bedroom with an en-suite master bathroom, spacious mud room, a large open-concept kitchen and living area, a second family room, full bathroom and a warm and cozy dining room.  There is an addition that offers four addition rooms, all currently being used as bedrooms.  Upstairs you will find two additional bedrooms.  The large, 2-story barn interior is in solid shape, with a large separate office and ample storage, grow rooms, horse stalls and so much more.  The third barn can be used as a garage and provides even more space for the adventurous minds.  Come take a look at this beautiful property and make it your own!
